dct:title.value: A new subspecies of Trypoxylus dichotomus (Coleoptera: scarabaeidae: dynastinae) from China

bibo:abstract.value: This paper describes Trypoxylus dichotomus shennongji subsp. nov., the 6th subspecies of T. dichotomus Linnaeus (1771) from Shennongjia, Hubei Province, China, whose diagnostic illustrations with a distribution map are provided.
